				<link>http://www.hvaonline.net/hvaonline/posts/preList/28184/173273.hva#173273</link>
				<pubDate><![CDATA[Sun, 15 Mar 2009 04:13:38]]> GMT</pubDate>
				<author><![CDATA[ giobuon]]></author>
